stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> init: 启动
    init --> snapshot: initializeVersionedPlugins\n（V1→V2迁移 + 快照）
    snapshot --> installed: addInstalledPlugin\n（安装写入磁盘）
    installed --> diverged: updateInstallationPathOnDisk\n（后台更新仅写磁盘）
    diverged --> synced: 用户重启 / reload-plugins\n（快照与磁盘重新同步）
    installed --> scope_removed: removePluginInstallation\n（按 scope 移除）
    scope_removed --> last_scope: isLastScope = true\n（所有 scope 都移除）
    scope_removed --> installed: isLastScope = false\n（其他 scope 仍在）
    last_scope --> cleanup: markPluginVersionOrphaned\n+ deletePluginOptions\n+ deletePluginDataDir
    cleanup --> [*]
    synced --> installed
